   "label": "How to use"
  },
  {
   "fieldname": "intro_html",
   "fieldtype": "HTML",
    "options": "<div style='padding:8px;background:#f5f7fa;border-radius:6px;line-height:1.7'><b>Asset Bulk Import</b><br/>Upload an Excel (<code>.xlsx</code>) or CSV file with the following columns (case-insensitive, in any order):<ul style='margin:6px 0 0 18px'><li><b>Asset Name</b> (required, unique)</li><li><b>Item Name</b> (required - used to find / auto-create Item)</li><li><b>Category</b> (required - Asset Category, auto-created if missing)</li><li><b>Location</b> (required - auto-created if missing; e.g. <code>Ruwi Branch - Customer Hall - VIP Room</code>)</li><li><b>Company</b> (required - must exist in the system)</li><li><b>RFID Tag</b> (required, unique)</li><li><b>Images</b> (optional - one or more file URLs separated by <code>,</code> or <code>|</code>; e.g. <code>/files/img1.jpg, /files/img2.jpg</code>)</li></ul>Item Code is auto-generated from Item Name. Item Group and Asset Category are auto-created from Category. Company is applied to the Asset, Location, Category and Item.</div>"
